# Symphony + Codex Windows 快速启动手册

## 1. 进入项目

```bash
cd /e/project/AginLG/symphony/symphony/elixir
```

确认目录：

```bash
ls
```

应该看到：

```text
WORKFLOW.md
AGENTS.md
mix.exs
bin
```

---

## 2. 安装依赖

首次安装：

```bash
mix deps.get
```

---

## 3. 编译

```bash
mix build
```

成功后会出现：

```text
Generated escript bin/symphony
```

---

## 4. 配置 Codex

WORKFLOW.md：

```yaml
codex:
  command: codex --yolo app-server -c shell_environment_policy.inherit=all -c 'model="gpt-5.5"' -c model_reasoning_effort=xhigh
  read_timeout_ms: 120000
  approval_policy: never
  thread_sandbox: workspace-write
  turn_sandbox_policy:
    type: workspaceWrite
```

---

## 5. 检查 Codex

```bash
codex --version
```

应该看到：

```text
0.135.x
```

检查：

```bash
codex app-server --help
```

正常显示帮助即可。

---

## 6. 启动 Symphony

```bash
bin/symphony --i-understand-that-this-will-be-running-without-the-usual-guardrails WORKFLOW.md
```

---

## 7. Linear 状态配置

Linear 当前状态：

```text
Backlog
Planned
In Progress
Completed
Canceled
```

WORKFLOW.md 中必须匹配：

```yaml
active_states:
  - Backlog
  - Planned
  - In Progress
```

否则 Symphony 抓不到 Issue。

---

## 8. 新建 Issue

例如：

```text
BUZ-18

创建 Next.js 项目

Acceptance Criteria

- 初始化 Next.js
- 配置 Tailwind
- 配置 ESLint
- pnpm dev 正常启动
```

状态：

```text
Backlog
```

---

## 9. Workspace 目录

Symphony 会创建：

```text
C:\Users\Administrator\code\symphony-workspaces\
```

例如：

```text
BUZ-18
```

---

## 10. 查看运行状态

Linear：

```text
Backlog
↓
In Progress
```

出现：

```text
Codex Workpad
```

说明正常。

---

## 11. 删除缓存重新执行

停止：

```bash
Ctrl + C
```

删除：

```bash
rm -rf /c/Users/Administrator/code/symphony-workspaces/BUZ-18
```

重新启动：

```bash
bin/symphony --i-understand-that-this-will-be-running-without-the-usual-guardrails WORKFLOW.md
```

---

## 12. 常用排查

### 看日志

```bash
tail -f log/dev.log
```

### 看 Workspace

```bash
cd /c/Users/Administrator/code/symphony-workspaces/BUZ-18
git status
```

### 看 Codex Session

```text
C:\Users\Administrator\.codex\sessions\
```

查看最新 jsonl 文件。
